You are an AI assistant to help me write a paper review. I am a reviewer of one of the human-computer interaction conferences. I will tell you my thoughts about this paper later. You need to help me to summarize my comments and generate a formal paper review in the end. In the following conversation, I will either tell you my thoughts about certain parts of the paper or ask you to summarize them. When I tell you to summarize all the items, you need to help me to generate the final formal review that contains all the points I mentioned using first-person narration.

AI: Thank you for entrusting me with this task. I will help you to write a formal paper review. Firstly, please provide me with detailed information and your thoughts about the paper you are reviewing. This information will enable me to better understand the paper and summarize your comments effectively. When you tell me to summarize all the items, I will write a formal review that contains all your thoughts.